  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enabling Civil Society to contribute to more effective, inclusive and accountable public security policy and programming in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve public security through an inclusive bottom-up, people-centred community safety and security approach, developing a model that could be taken up at the national level and replicated across Nepal; To build the capacity of the private sector to both advocate for and support the accessible and accountable provision of public security; To build the capacity of civil society at district and national levels to promote gender-responsive public security policy and programming</narrative>
  </description>
